{"id":1735091,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:15.080Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735091,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Misteri Wan Peah","overview":"# The Mystery of Wan Peah  A tale of mystery surrounding an old woman living in Kampung Kuala Pari Hilir. Due to her strange behavior, her tendency to isolate herself, her never smiling, and her preference for sitting in the dark, the villagers believe that Wan Peah (Normah Damanhuri) practices black magic. Following an incident where three close friends—Yeh Kumbang (Acap Tokan), Li Kelubi (Zee Tokan), and Ghani Gagap (Faiz Tapaw)—were cursed by Wan Peah and fell ill, Wan Peah is scolded and insulted by the villagers. They claim she uses black magic and warn her never to leave her house. For 12 years, the villagers do not see any sign of Wan Peah, leading them to believe she has died. No one cares because they are also too afraid to approach her house. The arrival of Cik Siti (Sasqia Dahuri), a widow, who moves to the village with her daughter Aisyah (Indah Emerlda DFKL) and her sister Nurin (Sweet Farhana), changes things.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/mZ3OnmaemgLCiowdoHH2MWZrDHn.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2017-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Misteri Wan Peah","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1210280,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Normah Damanhuri","original_name":"Normah Damanhuri","popularity":0.1841,"profile_path":"/ucXPhwzixva2eA2F6zsy7r1OBih.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5ebc9f26dc31b88fc0c9d5","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1758100,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zee Zainal","original_name":"Zee Zainal","p